# ========================================
# GITIGNORE FOR EPIC WIKI REPOSITORY
# ========================================
# This .gitignore excludes development files and large source files
# Only wiki content (markdown, images, data) and update scripts are published
# ========================================

# Python (exclude all except update scripts)
*.py
!update-wiki.py
__pycache__/
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
*.egg

# PowerShell (exclude all except update scripts)
*.ps1
!update-wiki.ps1

# Virtual environments
venv/
env/
ENV/
.venv/

# IDE and Editor files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

# Obsidian vault metadata (usually not published)
.obsidian/

# OS files
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# Temporary and log files
*.tmp
*.bak
*.log
*.cache

# PDF source documents (excluded to reduce repo size)
*.pdf

# PDF extracted page directories
*_Pages/
*_Pages

# Problematic file that can't be indexed by git
RULES/Skills/LUCK/Con.md

# Elf variant files (to be updated)
Creatures/Humanoids/Forces of Good/Elves/Black-Elf.md
Creatures/Humanoids/Forces of Good/Elves/Desert-Elf.md
Creatures/Humanoids/Forces of Good/Elves/Ice-Elf.md
Creatures/Humanoids/Forces of Good/Elves/Jungle-Elf.md
Creatures/Humanoids/Forces of Good/Elves/Mountain-Elf.md
Creatures/Humanoids/Forces of Good/Elves/Sea-Elf.md
Creatures/Humanoids/Forces of Good/Elves/Wild-Elf.md

# Tools directory (large files)
tools/

# ========================================
# EXPLICITLY INCLUDED (Published to GitHub)
# ========================================
# Wiki content files that ARE tracked and published:
# - *.md (Markdown wiki pages)
# - *.png, *.jpg, *.jpeg, *.gif (Images)
# - *.json (Data files and configurations)
# - *.txt (Text files)
# - update-wiki.bat, update-wiki.ps1 (Update scripts)
# - !update-wiki.py (if we create a Python update script)
# - !update-wiki.ps1 (PowerShell update script)
# ========================================
